Nightly from 9 45  P M until 1 30 A M buses replace trains between Central and Circular Quay via Museum.
T 2 Leppington, T 3 Bankstown and T 8 Airport & South Line trains start and end at Central.
T 1 Western, T 2 Inner West and T 9 Northern Line trains continue to run between Central and Wynyard.
